        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I'd like to mention that if `:restart` is made to respect `'confirm'`, it might make sense for `:restart` to default to `+qall` instead of `+qall!` in all cases, since I think it would be unintuitive for the `'confirm'` option to affect whether modifications are discarded without prompting, when the option will normally affect commands that would othereise fail, not otherwise succeed.\n\nThen again, as long as the current behavior can be recreated with `:restart +qall!`, it doesn't matter too much. Just my two cents.",
